<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Course Purchase Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        /* Insert your CSS styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Course Purchase Confirmation</h2>
        <p>Dear User,</p>
        <p>We're delighted to inform you that you have successfully enrolled in the "<%= order.name %>" course! Here are
                the details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Order ID:</strong>
                <%= order._id %>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Course:</strong>
                <%= order.name %>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Instructor:</strong> Darshan Thakkar</li>
            <li><strong>Price:</strong>
                <%= order.price %>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>You now have access to the course materials and resources. Start learning and enhancing your skills right away!
        </p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to <a href="darshanthakkar782@gmail.com">contact
                our support team</a>.</p>
        <p>Happy learning!</p>
        <a href="#" class="button">Access Your Course</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
